    "lyrics": {
      "text": "Awed by the__ beau--------ty____ of thy__ vir--gin----i-ty and the re-splend----en--cy____ of thy great pu------ri-ty, the an-gel Gab-ri-el__ called___ out__ to thee___ thus,___ O The--o-to-----kos:__ What____ wor-thy__ hymn_____ of___ praise____ can I of---fer__ un-----to thee? How__ shall I re--fer to____ thee?__ I am caught____ in be-wil-der-ment.__ And there-fore as__ com-mand---ed,___ I cry___ out: Maid--en full__ of grace,___ re-joice___ thou.__"
